These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
House: wooden, modern, palace, farmhouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, february, march
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, orange, chestnut, grey
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, go, canasta
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, hedgehog, dog
 1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 2. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
 7. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 8. the person playing go is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
 9. the owner of the dog is the wooden house##1
10. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
11. the modern house is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
13. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the palace house##8
14. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
15. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
16. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| House    | farmhouse | modern     | palace     | wooden |
| Birthday        | september  | november | february      | march      |
| Color         | grey  | orange    | chestnut | coral       |
| Game       | snooker | mah-jongg   | go      | canasta  |
| Pet   | rat      | bird  | hedgehog   | dog      |

